{"name": "d0da", "metadata": {"name": "d0da", "version": "0.9.0", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: GNU General Public License v3 (GPLv3)", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13"], "home_page": null, "license": "GPL-3.0", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["click", "protobuf"], "summary": "Wooting D0DA protocol", "upload_time": 1735845477}, "documentation": ["# Wooting D0DA Protocol\n\n## Introduction\n\nWooting has been very generous in supplying Open Source (!) SDKs for their hardware, only, the SDKs aren't\nvery thoroughly documented, limited to a single use case and written in C.\n\nThis repository tries to fill in these gaps, it generated the packets and the used fields are described. It also\ndescribes what the packets do and in what order they should be sent.\n\n## Features\n\n- Technical documentation\n- Command line interface (d0da-cli) for sending packets to the keyboard\n- Unit tests\n\n## Limitations\n\n- Linux only (for now)\n- Wooting 60HE (ARM) only, though the packets should be compatible with other keyboards.\n\n## Installation\n\nRun:\n\n```bash\npipx install d0da\n```\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "d0da.d0da_report", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "d0da.d0da_report.set_upper_rows_rgb", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "row1", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "row2", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "row3", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Set the upper three rows of RGB leds.\n\nRows are an iterable of rgb values"]}, {"name": "d0da.d0da_report.set_lower_rows_rgb", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "row1", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "row2", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "row3", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Set the upper three rows of RGB leds.\n\nRows are an iterable of rgb values"]}, {"name": "d0da.d0da_report.set_brightness", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "brightness", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "a", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "b", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "c", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "d", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Set brightness"]}, {"name": "d0da.d0da_report.rgb_array_update_keyboard", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "*args", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Update RGB array of keyboard.\n\nargs should be encoded as:\n\nencode |= (red & 0xf8) << 8;\nencode |= (green & 0xfc) << 3;\nencode |= (blue & 0xf8) >> 3;\n\nThis is only supported after calling woot_dev_init."]}, {"name": "d0da.d0da_report.keymap", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["d0 da 14 01 02 00 00 96 0a 17 0a 15 ff ff ff ff\nff ff ff ff ff ff ff ff ff ff ff ff ff ff ff ff\nff 0a 17 0a 15 32 37 38 39 3a 3b 3c 3d 3e 3f 40\n41 42 49 ff ff ff ff ff ff ff 0a 17 0a 15 c3 c5\n\nc4 c1 c2 c0 ff ff 4f 44 43 48 47 ff ff ff ff ff\nff ff ff 0a 17 0a 15 36 ff ff ff ff e1 e0 4d 4e\n4c 4b 4a ff e6 ff ff ff ff ff ff ff 0a 17 0a 15\n64 ff ff ff ff ff ff ff ff d2 45 46 ff 68 ff ff\n\nff ff ff ff ff 0a 17 0a 15 63 66 65 ff ff ff ff\nff ff ff 69 ea 77 67 ff ff ff ff ff ff ff 00 00\n00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00\n00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"]}, {"name": "d0da.d0da_report.rgb_power_off", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "dim_minutes", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "off_minutes", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["enable:\nd0 da 17 00 08 0a 04 08 05 10 0a 10\n\ndisable:\nd0 da 17 00 02 10"]}], "variables": [{"name": "d0da.d0da_report.D0DA", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "d0da.hidraw", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name"